 Then transfer the resulting file to your PC.
 These files will be bigger than the floppies they were copied from; so
 you need a big RAMdrive to put them in.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Once you have the files on the PC in CPCEMU format, proceed as described
 in section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec: addboot"

\end_inset

, with pre-prepared disc images.
\end_layout

