\begin_layout Standard
The keyboard settings screen has five options.
 The first two are related to swapping keys: One controls which way round
 the CTRL and ALT keys are mapped (see section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec: keyswap"

\end_inset

